resources.string: "Susa ukuxhumanisa lo oxhumana naye umfake koxhumana nabo abaningi?"
"Ungathanda ukulondoloza ushintsho osuvele ulwenzile uphinde ususe ukuxhumana kwalo oxhumana naye kwiningi loxhumana nabo?"
"Ungathanda ukulondoloza ushintsho osuvele ulwenzile uphinde uxhumane noxhumana naye okhethiwe?"
"Lo oxhumana naye ufundeka kuphela. Angasuswa, kodwa akakwazi ukufihlwa."
"Oxhumana nabo kusukela kuma-akhawunti wakho wokufunda kuphela abakwazi ukususwa, kodwa bangafihlwa."
"Oxhumana nabo abazosuswa banemininingwane esuka kuma-akhawunti amaningi. Imininingwane esuka kuma-akhawunti wokufunda kuphela izofihlwa, ngeke isuswe."
"Ukususa lo oxhumana naye kuzosusa iminingwane kusukela kuma-akhawunti amaningi."
"Alukho uhlelo lokusebenza olutholakalele ukuphatha lesi senzo."
"Shintshela ekuhleleni othintana naye okhethiwe? Ulwazi olufakile kuze kube manje luzokopishwa."
"Susa ilebula engu-\"%1$s\"? (Oxhumana nabo ngokwabo ngeke baze basuswe.)"
"Bhala igama lomuntu oxhumana naye ngaphambili kokujoyina nomunye."
"Thatha iminithi ukungeza i-akhawunti ezokwenza isipele oxhumana nabo ku-Google."
"Laba oxhumana nabo kungaba umuntu ofanayo. Ungabaxhumanisa ndawonye njengoxhumana naye oyedwa."
"Uzosula uhlu loxhumana nabo kakhulu kuzinhelo zokusebenza zokuxhumana noma zefoni, futhi uphoqelele izinhlelo zokusebenza ze-imeyili ukufunda izintandokazi zakho zekheli kusuka ekuqaleni."
"Bonke othintana nabo kanye nezinombolo zabo zocingo"
"Iyasusa \"%s\" kokuvumelanisiwe izophinde isuse nanoma ibaphi oxhumana nabo abangelona iqoqo."
"Iqedile ukuthumela oxhumana nabo, chofoza isaziso ukuze wabelane ngoxhumana nabo."
"Isicelo sokungenisa i-vCard sinqatshelwe. Sicela uzame futhi emva kwesikhathi."
"Isicelo sokuthekelisa i-vCard sinqatshelwe. Sicela uzame futhi emva kwesikhathi."
"Ifihla i-vCard/ama-vCard endaweni yokugcina eseduze. Ukulandwa kwangampela kuzoqala khona maduze."
"Lona oxhumana naye ngeke ukwazi ukwabelana ngaye."
"Izinguquko ozenzayo kuzo zonke izinhlelo zokusebenza nama-akhawunti, hhayi oxhumana nabo nje kuphela, zizohlala zibuyekezwa phakathi kwewebhu namadivayisi akho."
"Ayikwazanga ukungenisa oxhumana nabo kusukela ku-SIM card"
